It would be ideal to have a system property to disable the "Distribute to Bintray" right click option on artifacts and folders in the UI. Since not everyone uses bintray, having that option there is just confusing and clutters up the config. However, an easy compromise seems to be just to add a custom property to the artifactory.system.properties file to disable this.

For example, the current system properties available for this are:
{code}
artifactory.bintray.ui.hideUploads=true
artifactory.bintray.ui.hideInfo=true
artifactory.bintray.ui.hideRemoteSearch=true
{code}

I propose adding:
{code}
artifactory.bintray.ui.hideRightClick=true
{code}

