14/Jun/16 9:25 AM;aldaris;I wrote a groovy plugin in the end:
{noformat}
download {
    def exposedRepositories = ['private-releases']

    afterDownloadError { request -> 
        if (security.isAnonymous()) {
            if (exposedRepositories.contains(request.repoPath.repoKey)) {
                if (repositories.exists(request.repoPath)) {
                    // By returning 403 we ensure that Artifactory will send WWW-Authenticate header in its response
                    // In other words this 403 will magically turn into 401
                    status = 403
                    message = "Unauthorized"
                } else {
                    status = 404
                    message = "File not found."
                }
            }
        }
    }
}
{noformat}
